#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-08-hidden-cost-rootless-container-networking.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Why isn't Quarkus 2x faster than Spring on my machine?"
msgstr "为什么在我的机器上，Quarkus 没有比 Spring 快 2 倍？"

#. type: YAML Front Matter: synopsis
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-08-hidden-cost-rootless-container-networking.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Our perf-lab shows Quarkus 2x faster than Spring, but a community member only sees 1.19x locally. The culprit: a userspace TCP proxy hidden inside rootless podman."
msgstr "我们的性能实验室显示 Quarkus 比 Spring 快 2 倍，但一位社区成员在本地只看到 1.19 倍。罪魁祸首是隐藏在无根 podman 中的用户空间 TCP 代理。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-08-hidden-cost-rootless-container-networking.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "A community member ran our https://github.com/quarkusio/spring-quarkus-perf-comparison[Quarkus vs Spring CRUD benchmark] on their bare-metal Fedora workstation and asked:"
msgstr "一位社区成员在他们的裸机 Fedora 工作站上运行了我们的 link:https://github.com/quarkusio/spring-quarkus-perf-comparison[Quarkus vs Spring CRUD 基准] ，并提出了一个问题："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-08-hidden-cost-rootless-container-networking.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "_Why do I see only 1.19x instead of 2x?_"
msgstr "_为什么我只看到 1.19 倍而不是 2 倍？_"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-08-hidden-cost-rootless-container-networking.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Our perf-lab shows Quarkus at 2.08x Spring's throughput, but locally the gap nearly disappears.**"
msgstr "*我们的性能实验室显示，Quarkus 的吞吐量是 Spring 的 2.08 倍，但在局部地区，差距几乎消失。*"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-08-hidden-cost-rootless-container-networking.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This post walks through the investigation that found the culprit."
msgstr "这篇文章将介绍找到罪魁祸首的调查过程。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-08-hidden-cost-rootless-container-networking.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The gap"
msgstr "差距"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-08-hidden-cost-rootless-container-networking.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The benchmark is a REST/CRUD application backed by PostgreSQL. The app runs on the host, PostgreSQL in a rootless podman container. Each HTTP request executes 2 SQL queries (confirmed via https://www.postgresql.org/docs/current/pgstatstatements.html[pg_stat_statements])."
msgstr "该基准是一个由 PostgreSQL 支持的 REST/CRUD 应用程序。应用程序在主机上运行，PostgreSQL 在无根 podman 容器中运行。每个 HTTP 请求执行 2 个 SQL 查询（通过 link:https://www.postgresql.org/docs/current/pgstatstatements.html[pg_stat_statements] 确认）。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-08-hidden-cost-rootless-container-networking.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Spring delivers roughly the same throughput in both environments. Quarkus swings from 15.5K to 24.5K TPS — it is being held back locally. **Something in the local environment is capping Quarkus but not Spring.**"
msgstr "Spring 在两种环境下的吞吐量大致相同。Quarkus 的吞吐量从 15.5K 增至 24.5K - 它在本地受到了限制。 *本地环境中的某些因素限制了 Quarkus，但没有限制 Spring。*"

