#: _posts/2026-06-08-hidden-cost-rootless-container-networking.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "To measure pasta's impact on database traffic, we ran https://www.postgresql.org/docs/current/pgbench.html[pgbench] with the same 2-query workload (50 clients — matching the default JDBC connection pool size for both Quarkus and Spring — prepared statements, 30 seconds) over different network paths. We also tested with Fedora's https://wiki.nftables.org/[nftables] firewall disabled, since the flamegraph showed `nft_do_chain` in the kernel stacks:"
msgstr "为了衡量 pasta 对数据库流量的影响，我们在不同的网络路径上运行了 link:https://www.postgresql.org/docs/current/pgbench.html[pgbench] ，测试了相同的 2-query 工作负载（50 个客户端--与 Quarkus 和 Spring 的默认 JDBC 连接池大小相匹配--准备语句，30 秒）。我们还禁用了 Fedora 的 link:https://wiki.nftables.org/[nftables] 防火墙进行测试，因为 flamegraph 显示内核堆栈中存在 `nft_do_chain` ："

